      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ETHAN'S BROTHER (1) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at Q Straight in a handy 19.14 beating Hara's Max. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Can continue the winning form. ZIPPING MEHARY (2) jumped from a middle draw last time and could manage only fifth and beaten 4.5 lengths (20.25) at Capalaba. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Bold showing expected. ETERNITY BRIDGE (3) was below latest but prior to that a Grade 5 winner in quick time (30.03) at this track in a Grade 5. Can improve sharply here. MALAWI REBEL (7) was out of placings last time (25.62) at Q Lakeside in a OPEN, finishing sixth and beaten 11 lengths. Has already won out of this draw.",
